'''位智'''（{{lang-en|Waze}}）是一个基于[[GPS|GPS]]的导航[[移动软件应用程序|移动软件应用程序]]，其利用{{link-en|turn-by-turn导航|turn-by-turn navigation}}以及用户提交的出行时间和路线详情。Waze由[[以色列|以色列]]的Waze Mobile开发，已经由[[Google|Google]]于2013年收购（尽管美国联邦贸易委员会和英国的监管部门正在考虑[[Google|Google]]的收购是否可能违反了反垄断法）。

Waze在2013年的[[全球行動通訊大會|全球行動通訊大會]]上赢得了最佳整体移动应用程序奖，赢得该奖项的还有[[Dropbox|Dropbox]]、[[Flipboard|Flipboard]]等。<ref name="globes-bestapp">{{cite news|url=http://www.globes.co.il/serveen/globes/docview.asp?did=1000825700&fid=1725|title=Waze wins Best Mobile App award in Barcelona|author=Hoffman, Tzahi|work=[[Globes|Globes]]|date=February 27, 2013|accessdate=February 28, 2013|archive-date=2013-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004062204/http://www.globes.co.il/serveen/globes/docview.asp?did=1000825700&fid=1725|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年6月11日，[[Google|Google]]以10.3亿[[美元|美元]]完成了对Waze的收购。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://googleblog.blogspot.com/2013/06/google-maps-and-waze-outsmarting.html|title=Google Maps and Waze, outsmarting traffic together|accessdate=11 June 2013|archive-date=2013-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130727061330/http://googleblog.blogspot.com/2013/06/google-maps-and-waze-outsmarting.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Chan, Edwin.  [http://www.jewishjournal.com/science_and_technology/article/google_buys_israels_waze_to_protect_mobile_maps_lead "Google buys Israel’s Waze to protect mobile maps lead."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jewishjournal.com/science_and_technology/article/google_buys_israels_waze_to_protect_mobile_maps_lead |date=20161126134714 }} ''Jewish Journal''.  11 June 2013.  11 June 2013.</ref>作为签署协议的一部分，Waze 100名员工平均都将收到120万美元，这是以色列高科技历史上最大的员工奖励。<ref>{{cite news|last=Teig|first=Amir|title=Waze employees clinch most lucrative exit in Israeli history|url=http://www.haaretz.com/business/waze-s-100-employees-to-get-an-average-of-1-2-million-each.premium-1.529478/|accessdate=25 June 2013|newspaper=Haaretz|date=June 13, 2013|archive-date=2013-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130715232037/http://www.haaretz.com/business/waze-s-100-employees-to-get-an-average-of-1-2-million-each.premium-1.529478|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Waze支持[[Android|Android]]、[[iPhone|iPhone]]、[[Symbian|Symbian]]、[[Blackberry_10|Blackberry 10]]，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://world.waze.com/faq/ |title=Waze FAQs |publisher=World.waze.com |date= |accessdate=2013-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130708113343/http://world.waze.com/faq/ |archive-date=2013-07-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>以及[[Windows_Mobile|Windows Mobile]] 5–6<ref>[http://www.waze.com/support/ Waze Support, Quick Help.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.waze.com/support/ |date=20130722125114 }} Type "Windows mobile" in search box. Shows "How to install Waze" with download for WM5-6 on device from http://m.waze.com {{Wayback|url=http://m.waze.com/ |date=20160801000620 }}. Also Symbian and old Blackberry.</ref>。2013年5月，[[Windows_Phone_8|Windows Phone 8]]的测试版可在[[Windows_Phone_Store|Windows Phone Store]]上下载。<ref>Kee, Edwin May 21, 2013. "Waze Arrives At Windows Phone Store" http://www.ubergizmo.com/2013/05/waze-arrives-at-windows-phone-store/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.ubergizmo.com/2013/05/waze-arrives-at-windows-phone-store/ |date=20130728210556 }}</ref> {{As of|2013|7}}，Waze称他们目前正在计划同时支持iPhone及Android，并将推出更多平台的版本。较旧的平台（Symbian、WM、Blackberry）将不支持一个完整的原生UI或其他的API，但现有版本将继续工作。<ref>[http://www.waze.com/support/ Waze Support, Quick Help.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.waze.com/support/ |date=20130722125114 }} Type "Future waze versions" in search box. Shows "Future waze versions and operating systems". States that current versions for WM, BB and Symbian will continue to be available.</ref>

