== 概述 ==
[[File:Waze_3.5_Screen.png|thumb]]
Waze与传统的{{link-en|GPS导航软件|GPS navigation software}}的不同之处在于它是一个由社区驱动，收集用户的地图数据和其他信息，并学习用户的驾驶时间，提供路线和实时路况更新的应用程序。<ref>{{cite web |last=Terdiman |first=Daniel |url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-13772_3-10305132-52.html |title=CNET News - Waze iPhone app provides real-time, crowdsourced traffic data |publisher=News.cnet.com |date=2009-08-06 |accessdate=2012-09-25 |archive-date=2012-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120901014951/http://news.cnet.com/8301-13772_3-10305132-52.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>其下载与使用均是免费的。人们可以报告事故、交通堵塞、速度和警察，并能更新道路、地标、门牌号码等。Waze还可以根据用户的报告，确定附近最便宜的加油站。{{Asof|2012年1月}}，该应用程序在全球已被下载1200万次。<ref name="forbes">Devindra Hardawar. [http://www.forbes.com/sites/tomiogeron/2011/10/18/waze-nabs-30m-from-kleiner-perkins-li-ka-shing-mary-meeker-to-advise/ Waze raises $30M for its crowdsourced driving app, hits 7M users] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DFjI93vh?url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/tomiogeron/2011/10/18/waze-nabs-30m-from-kleiner-perkins-li-ka-shing-mary-meeker-to-advise/ |date=20121228171841 |dateformat=iso }}. Forbes, October 18, 2011</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Gilbert|first=Jason|title=Waze, A Free GPS Driving App, Features Spoken Turn-By-Turn Directions And User Input|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/02/08/waze-free-gps-driving-app_n_1263724.html|newspaper=The Huffington Post|date=9 Feb 2012|accessdate=2013-07-28|archive-date=2014-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104205622/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/02/08/waze-free-gps-driving-app_n_1263724.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年7月，Waze宣布，其已经达到了2000万用户，其中一半是在过去六个月中获得的。<ref>Lardinois, Frederic. July 5, 2012. "Waze Doubles Its User Base To 20 Million In 6 Months." http://techcrunch.com/2012/07/05/waze-20-million/ {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/07/05/waze-20-million/ |date=20130729140515 }}</ref>根据Yahoo!，Waze的用户数在2013年1月已近5000万。<ref>Yahoo.com, June 12, 2013 "Waze sale signals new growth for Israeli high tech" http://news.yahoo.com/waze-sale-signals-growth-israeli-high-tech-174533585.html {{Wayback|url=http://news.yahoo.com/waze-sale-signals-growth-israeli-high-tech-174533585.html |date=20130816080341 }}</ref>

Waze可以在世界上任何地方使用；但只有13个城市城市有完整的地图，其他城市的地图均未完成，需要大量用户记录并编辑地图。{{As of|2013}}，Waze已经完成了美国、加拿大、英国、法国、德国、意大利、荷兰、比利时、以色列（地图在这些地国家最完整<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WWP4oTSEv5A |title=Community car GPS navigation - WAZE - at DEMOfall09 |publisher=YouTube |date=2009-09-27 |accessdate=2012-09-25 |archive-date=2014-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125210138/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WWP4oTSEv5A |dead-url=no }}</ref>），南非<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.waze.com/blog/waze-launches-in-south-africa/ |title=Waze Blog - Waze launches in South Africa |publisher=Waze.com |date=2012-03-14 |accessdate=2012-09-25 |archive-date=2012-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120919010853/http://www.waze.com/blog/waze-launches-in-south-africa/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>厄瓜多尔、阿根廷、智利和巴拿马。公司已经在计划完成欧洲及世界各地其他国家的地图。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.waze.com/blog/waze-now-available-internationally/ |title=Waze Blog - Waze now available internationally – put your country on the map! |publisher=Waze.com |date=2009-11-10 |accessdate=2012-09-25 |archive-date=2013-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130604055527/http://www.waze.com/blog/waze-now-available-internationally/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.waze.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=18&t=2885 |title=Waze Forum - European Maps Schedule Update |publisher=Waze.com |date= |accessdate=2012-09-25 |archive-date=2012-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304080722/http://www.waze.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=18&t=2885 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

除了turn-by-turn语音导航、实时路况，以及其他特定位置的警报，Waze同时发送匿名信息，其中包括用户的速度和位置。信息返回到其数据库以完善服务。该[[众包|众包]]项目允许Waze社群简单地报告导航及地图错误、交通事故，但为了安全，会要求用户停下车或确定自己是乘客才能完成一些操作。Waze使用游戏机制以鼓励用户提供更多交通信息换取积分，通过积分可以更改驾驶时在公开地图上的头像图标等，并能提升等级。<ref>{{cite web |last=Furchgott |first=Roy |url=http://wheels.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/05/06/filling-in-the-map-gaps-with-waze-games/ |title=Waze in a New York Times blog |publisher=Wheels.blogs.nytimes.com |date=2010-05-06 |accessdate=2012-09-25 |archive-date=2013-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130104153738/http://wheels.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/05/06/filling-in-the-map-gaps-with-waze-games/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2011年，Waze移动更新了软件，可实时显示，社区策划的兴趣点，包括当地的活动，如街头集市和抗议。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/g/a/2011/10/13/prweb8877577.DTL |title=Waze Introduces Redesigned App for iPad, iPhone & iPod touch, Steering Drivers from Local Search to Local Discovery |publisher=Sfgate.com |date=2011-10-13 |accessdate=2012-09-25}}</ref>

在2012年6月，Waze推出更新，提供实时燃料价格。Waze实时更新的价格是由用户提交的。<ref>Ha, Anthony. June 20, 2012. "Navigation App Waze Adds Real-Time Fuel Prices." http://techcrunch.com/2012/06/20/waze-fuel/ {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/06/20/waze-fuel/ |date=20130728085738 }}</ref>

2012年11月以来，Waze开始用应用程序盈利，Waze提供经销商和广告商一个web界面发布广告，广告基于地图上的小图标。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.adweek.com/news/technology/waze-maps-out-native-ad-platform-145035 |title=Waze Maps Out Native Ad Platform Driving app navigates direct sales, self-serve |publisher=adweek.com |date=2012-11-07 |accessdate=2013-06-18 |archive-date=2013-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601014443/http://www.adweek.com/news/technology/waze-maps-out-native-ad-platform-145035 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其还提供新闻电视台一个接口以直接从Waze获取当前交通报告；此服务在2013年6月被25个美国新闻电视台使用。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/parmyolson/2013/06/13/what-waze-adds-to-google-a-view-from-wazes-ceo/ |title=What Waze Adds To Google: A View From Waze's CEO |publisher=forbes.com |date=2013-06-13 |accessdate=2013-06-13 |archive-date=2013-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617041220/http://www.forbes.com/sites/parmyolson/2013/06/13/what-waze-adds-to-google-a-view-from-wazes-ceo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2013年6月，Waze推出了全球本地化项目，将在特定国家重大活动期间实时更新未来封路及交通状态，例如[[环法自行车赛|环法自行车赛]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.waze.com/blog/how-to-beat-epic-traffic-caused-by-summer-events/ |title=Waze Blog: How to Beat Epic Traffic Caused by Summer Events |publisher=waze.com |date=2013-06-27 |accessdate=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2013-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130710183323/http://www.waze.com/blog/how-to-beat-epic-traffic-caused-by-summer-events/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

